did.unittitle: Wisconsin. State Board of Assessors: Appeal Files, 19921994
did.physdesc: 2.0 c.f. (2 record center cartons); plus additions of 1.4 c.f.

physloc.extref: See the catalog entry for information of possible additional materials and shelf locations.

did.abstract: Records of appeals made to the State Board of Assessors under Wis. Stats. 70.995(8)(c) or (d), generally consisting of the original objection form filed by appellants, associated correspondence, and documentation of the Boards actions. The appeals were filed by individuals or corporations objecting to the amount, valuation, or taxability of manufacturing property, or to penalties issued for late or nonfiling of property report forms.

arrangement.p: This collection was received in multiple parts and is organized into 2 major parts. These materials have not been physically interfiled and researchers might need to consult more than one part to locate similar materials.
